line_1: Where with her Calf She chew'd the grateful Cud;
line_2: Or the calm Shelter of the cooler Wood,

line_1: And unmolested Kine rechew the Cud;
line_2: When nibbling Sheep at large pursue their Food,

line_1: The filthy Beasts, that never chew the Cud,
line_2: Even so through Brentford Town, a Town of Mud,

line_1: Osiris, Apis, Pow'rs that chew the Cud,
line_2: And Dog Anubis, Flatt'rer for his Food:
